headline: Molson Coors (TAP) Stock Is Up, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of beer company Molson Coors (NYSE:TAP) jumped 3.6% in the afternoon session after the company announced its Madrí Excepcional brand surpassed £1 billion in annual sales as the brand celebrated its fifth anniversary.
